      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.619 - The Messenger of Allah (sw) said:\n\"Whoever is overly cautious about his clothing during prayer (focusing excessively on keeping it clean or arranged), is not truly clothing himself for Allah (swt)”."
